usdnMapping:
- kind: ethereum/contract
    name: USDN
    network: mainnet
    source:
      address: "0x674C6Ad92Fd080e4004b2312b45f796a192D27a0"
      startBlock: 10970706
      abi: USDN
    mapping:
      kind: ethereum/events
      apiVersion: 0.0.7
      language: wasm/assemblyscript
      entities:
        - TokenSnapshot
      abis:
        - name: USDN
          file: ./abis/USDN.json
      eventHandlers:
        - event: Reward(uint256,uint256)
          handler: handleUsdnRewards
      file: ./src/services/rebase/mappingUsdn.ts
aethMapping:
- kind: ethereum/contract
    name: AETH
    network: mainnet
    source:
      address: "0x6a9366f02B6E252e0cbe2E6B9CF0a8adDd7B641C"
      startBlock: 10970706
      abi: AETH
    mapping:
      kind: ethereum/events
      apiVersion: 0.0.7
      language: wasm/assemblyscript
      entities:
        - TokenSnapshot
      abis:
        - name: AETH
          file: ./abis/AETH.json
      eventHandlers:
        - event: RatioUpdate(uint256)
          handler: handleAethRewards
      file: ./src/services/rebase/mappingAeth.ts
